#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/animal_friendship.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action    \n"
"**Range:** 30 feet    \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (a morsel of food)    \n"
"**Duration:** 24 hours\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/animal_friendship.md:17
msgid ""
"This spell lets you convince a beast that you mean it no harm. Choose a "
"beast that you can see within range. It must see and hear you. If the "
"beast's Intelligence is 4 or higher, the spell fails. Otherwise, the beast "
"must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be charmed by you for the spell's "
"duration. If you or one of your companions harms the target, the spells "
"ends."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/animal_friendship.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**At Higher Levels.** When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd "
"level or higher, you can affect one additional beast t level above 1st.\n"
